%h1 Blog

- @posts.each do |post|

  %div.box.blog
    %div.title= post.title
    %p= post.body

  = link_to 'Show', post#disqus_thread
  \|
  = link_to 'Edit', edit_post_path(post)
  \|
  = link_to 'Destroy', post, :confirm => 'Are you sure?', :method => :delete

